data.description: If you are looking for the perfect home in a golf course community golf, fish and ski look no further. This 2 bedroom 2 bath split floor plan has new appliances, a new roof and a brand new septic system. It also has a new AC compressor, new carpet, new laminate and fresh paint.  Sliders from the dining room, family room and master bedroom lead out to the covered patio and 9 foot deep pool with a diving board . This close concept home has a wood burning fire place and sits on a half acre of land. Be sure to take your cart the 19th Hole Bar and Grill. Other amenities include 9 & 18 hole golf courses, shuffle board, tennis and basketball, 23,000 sq.ft. clubhouse, cafe, post office, churches, library & fitness room. Check out the 2 vitural tours.
